Again, the second one is
the person I would bet

00:38:38.150 --> 00:38:43.100
is going to weather that
economic storm a lot more.

00:38:43.100 --> 00:38:45.730
In my opinion, the
only search engine

00:38:45.730 --> 00:38:49.002
that could possibly
deliver better

00:38:49.002 --> 00:38:50.460
and more tailored
and more relevant

00:38:50.460 --> 00:38:54.620
search results than
