00:38:54.620 --> 00:38:57.730
It couldn't give you the results
on such a wide range of topics.

00:38:57.730 --> 00:39:00.560
But it can give you,
for very specific,

00:39:00.560 --> 00:39:03.010
highly, highly relevant
pieces of information

00:39:03.010 --> 00:39:04.990
such as, where is
there someone who

00:39:04.990 --> 00:39:08.600
might be looking to hire someone
with me, with my skill set?

