00:40:29.280 --> 00:40:30.850
Or it could be stored ill will.

00:40:30.850 --> 00:40:34.430
But let's just talk about
positive reputation for now.

00:40:34.430 --> 00:40:38.160
So if your positive reputation
is your stored goodwill

00:40:38.160 --> 00:40:44.070
with others, which then causes
them to reinterpret what you

00:40:44.070 --> 00:40:47.660
say, what you do more
positively as a result.

00:40:47.660 --> 00:40:49.870
If someone has a very
positive reputation,

00:40:49.870 --> 00:40:52.490
it only takes a small bit
of positivity from them.

00:40:52.490 --> 00:40:57.000
And then you sort of imbue all
of the rest of the positivity.

00:40:57.000 --> 00:40:59.960
Someone with a really
positive reputation

00:40:59.960 --> 00:41:03.540
can get far, far more access.

00:41:03.540 --> 00:41:06.980
And reputation is stored as
goodwill in relationships.

00:41:06.980 --> 00:41:09.760
But again, if you had a
hub-and-spoke kind of set

00:41:09.760 --> 00:41:16.500
up, where the relationships
between the different people

00:41:16.500 --> 00:41:19.200
that you were
closest to was weak,

00:41:19.200 --> 00:41:22.250
then goodwill that you'd
restore in one relationship

00:41:22.250 --> 00:41:24.820
wouldn't transfer to another.

00:41:24.820 --> 00:41:28.140
Because they don't have
goodwill with each other.

00:41:28.140 --> 00:41:34.550
So in a tribe, every time you
contribute or help someone

00:41:34.550 --> 00:41:36.360
along their self
development journey,

00:41:36.360 --> 00:41:38.720
or give them access to
a resource they needed,

00:41:38.720 --> 00:41:41.920
or offer them a
job, or offer them

00:41:41.920 --> 00:41:45.410
a connection, or an investor,
or a co-founder, whatever

00:41:45.410 --> 00:41:49.380
it is, each time
you do that, you

00:41:49.380 --> 00:41:51.640
get a positive
stored reputation,

00:41:51.640 --> 00:41:53.430
a positive stored
goodwill, in all

00:41:53.430 --> 00:41:54.770
of the members of the tribe.

00:41:54.770 --> 00:41:57.750
And it has this kind
of compounding effect

00:41:57.750 --> 00:42:00.850
so that your reputation
with that group of people

00:42:00.850 --> 00:42:03.740
can get actually
quite astronomical.

00:42:03.740 --> 00:42:09.760
And so we took one of the true
wealth assets, the tribe--

00:42:09.760 --> 00:42:11.720
of which there are three.

