00:47:06.030 --> 00:47:07.421
MICHAEL ELLSBERG: Yeah.

00:47:07.421 --> 00:47:07.920
Thank you.

00:47:07.920 --> 00:47:09.580
That's a great question.

00:47:09.580 --> 00:47:13.352
People ask us,
well, have you have

00:47:13.352 --> 00:47:14.810
you used this
