00:47:14.810 --> 00:47:17.310
talking about for 40 years?

00:47:17.310 --> 00:47:18.980
And the answer is no.

00:47:18.980 --> 00:47:21.800
I'm not even 40 years old yet.

00:47:21.800 --> 00:47:23.420
And so what is the basis?

00:47:23.420 --> 00:47:26.820
Why are we up here, feeling
like we have any credibility

00:47:26.820 --> 00:47:28.040
to talk about these things?

00:47:28.040 --> 00:47:32.390
Well, we have been using
this plan for about 15 years.

00:47:32.390 --> 00:47:36.340
And specifically,
the part where we

00:47:36.340 --> 00:47:40.110
feel we've realized the most
value and have something very,

00:47:40.110 --> 00:47:43.610
very tangible that is a
thing that we can point to,

00:47:43.610 --> 00:47:45.750
that's really adding
value to our lives,

00:47:45.750 --> 00:47:52.160
is the cultivation of a tribe--
specifically in the Bay Area.

00:47:52.160 --> 00:47:54.512
Mostly, also, we're
connected to New York.

00:47:54.512 --> 00:47:56.220
One thing that's really
important to note

00:47:56.220 --> 00:47:59.860
is it's not centered
around one person.

00:47:59.860 --> 00:48:03.420
So this isn't a cult. This isn't
